item.title: OK, i need help!

Sure u got jdk & not jre?

set JAVA_HOME=C:\Program\Java\jdk1.6.0_04 C:\apache-ant-1.7.0\bin\ant -buildfile .\build.xml @echo cls pause

Demonik/Divine

@echo off set PATH=%PATH%;C:\apache-ant-1.7.0\bin set JAVA_HOME=C:\Program\Java\jdk1.6.0_04 ant -buildfile .\build.xml cls ant pause

If your still having problems, Pm me your msn & i can teamview you 2 help get you online with your server.
